title: Trump Expects a Q Coup, What To Watch (Bo Burnham, Mare, More) 6.2.21
itunes:title: Trump Expects a Q Coup, What To Watch (Bo Burnham, Mare, More) 6.2.21
description:
In episode 921, Jack and guest host Danl Goodman are joined by Secretly Incredibly Fascinating host Alex Schmidt to discuss Blippi being replaced with a new actor, people still believing in QAnon, people not knowing how to act after the pandemic, how the weather effects covid, the box office, and more! Plus super producer Anna Hossnieh's streaming corner!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Blippi Actor Stevin John Is Replaced in Latest YouTube Episode, Leaving Fans Puzzled
  2. Trump is Reportedly Telling People He Will Be Reinstated as President By August
  3. Trump has been telling a number of people he’s in contact with that he expects he will get reinstated by August (no that isn’t how it works but simply sharing the information).
  4. At Texas event with QAnon ties, Louie Gohmert downplays Jan. 6: ‘It wasn’t just right-wing extremists’
  5. Man tackled after running onto court at Wizards-76ers game
  6. The One Thing You Need To Boost Productivity, Naturally
  7. Feeling Anxious About Returning To Post-Pandemic Society? You're Not Alone
  8. New York Weighs Whether To-Go Cocktails Should Stick Around Post-Pandemic
  9. ‘Open Air’ Effect Gave the South a Break From Covid-19 Spring Surge
  10. In time for summer, Europe sees dramatic fall in virus cases
  11. Box Office: A $57M Debut For ‘Quiet Place 2’ Is Great News For ‘Black Widow’ And ‘F9’
  12. LISTEN: Fousheé - Deep End
